data.description: Welcome to 6832 Arbor Ridge Drive.  This two bedroom, two bath home is conveniently located in the Highview area close to both shopping, and restaurants.  The first floor is an open concept with breakfast bar, dining area, and large living room.  Upstairs has an additional bedroom, full bath, and loft area perfect for office, or den.  Updates include AC and living room flooring.  Call for your private showing today!
